description.narrative: Support the establishment of a sound private, well-functioning, equitable financial sector that fulfills critical roles in a market economy, most importantly financial intermediation – the efficient generation and allocation of savings to their most productive use.

This award strives to support the establishment of a sound private, well-functioning, equitable financial sector that fulfills critical roles in a market economy. More specifically, this includes Ensure the organizational reform project has a well-documented set of objectives, goals, milestones, etc., so the reform may be done effectively and efficiently; Develop and implement a project management structure, with staff, plans, controls, and performance measures to successfully complete the current tender for a major IT systems upgrade..
